{"tid":1104554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發文揚言殺AV女優紗倉真菜　43歲男遭逮捕","createTime":"2019-04-13T08:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T11:29:12.000Z","uid":72009,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9bda4c941a4645c189827293a0eff23a10336b8e","tid":1104554,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"日本男子在《推特》發文揚言要殺害日本AV女優紗倉真菜，遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n據《朝日電視台》報導，居無定所、目前無職的的43歲男子矢澤春彦，3日在紗倉真菜的《推特》留言說要殺死她，「雖然是女的也無法原諒」、「把妳殺的半死不活」。隨後男子遭到警方逮捕，不過矢澤春彦否認犯行，日本警視廳將調查矢澤春彦的動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190413/1550050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190413%2F1550050&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=4f4841e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190413%2F1550050&h=f9e9a605\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190413/1550050</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190413/640_321a35b6a41da905178aa24142d23838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190413%2F640_321a35b6a41da905178aa24142d23838.jpg&h=e466dd59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190413/640_50b4c3d9040f7ec0142c3a4cf62e2b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190413%2F640_50b4c3d9040f7ec0142c3a4cf62e2b39.jpg&h=657b9188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />處男"},{"pid":"8427076f4b3e885b153fdbfff91e6a698e424ac5","tid":1104554,"uid":191352,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c17961b71052489db8a6abc476f89c88f770e3e8","tid":1104554,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"cited